data.description: Please ignore time on market..was sold twice to single buyers and cancelled due to personal reasons.  Beautiful views from golf lot, of lake, mountains, and sunsets.  AVM run 8/28 shows est appraisal value 533k & home sold next door at this. .  King sized split secondary br, vaulted ceilings, tile throughout is 3 years new. The inviting living room transitions seamlessly into a skylit great room accentuated by a cozy fireplace. Breathtaking lake and mountain views from the comfort of a covered patio in the relaxing backyard. Roof was replaced in 2016 and Heat/AC in 2013.  Have a comp without the golf lot that appraised @ 530 k..this home is an opportunity & great value. Mostly cosmetic repairs needed, call lister for details.
